Package pkgGamePiece

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Animal
    Inherited by Fish and Crustacean sub classes to be used in G2Model Defines update method, abstract methods, and other setters/getters Created on 11/1/2019
    Crustacean
    Crustacean - Used to create the crustaceans in game 2 Created on 11/12/2019
    Fish
    Intractable fish in G2, swim around and can be captured with net or picture taken with camera depending on species.
    G1Player
    used to create the controllable ship for the first game
    G2Player
    The player class for game 2.
    G3Player
    used to create G3Player objects in the game 3 Created on 11/1/2019
    GamePiece
    Super class for all GamePieces, which are objects to be used in models and passed to view to hold positions.
    Item
    Inherited by the non-PlayerChar GamePieces.
    Net
    Holds location as well as state of net for animation purposes Created on 11/14/2019
    Obstacle
    Used for the obstacles in minigame 1, the rocks and the ships.
    PlayerChar
    Abstract class that all player character classes will inherit from.
    Probe
    used to create probe objects in Game 3 for the maze.
